Package: rdota
Title: Functions to Get and Clean Data from the OpenDota API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Eric",
           family = "Ekholm",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "eric.ekholm@gmail.com")
Description: rdota provides a set of functions to get and process data from the OpenDota API. The package follows tidy data principles to the extent possible to make working with the data easier in R.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/ekholme/rdota
